msgctxt "QL_Electric_Relic_Arrival"
msgid ""
"You've arrived in the thieves' hideout! You can\n"
"sense many people waiting withinâ€”you would\n"
"be at a disadvantage if a fight were to\n"
"break out.\n"
"\n"
"Sneak into the hideout, and recover the\n"
"Gerudo chief's heirloom."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_Electric_Relic_Defeat"
msgid ""
"You defeated the Thunderblight Ganon\n"
"lurking deep within the\n"
"Divine Beast Vah Naboris!\n"
"\n"
"Urbosa's Divine Beast Vah Naboris has\n"
"taken up a position in the eastern region of\n"
"the Gerudo Desert.\n"
"\n"
"Make your way back to Gerudo Town, and\n"
"report to the chief of the Gerudo, Riju!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_Electric_Relic_Deliver"
msgid ""
"At last you are ready to take on the\n"
"Divine Beast Vah Naboris. Head for the\n"
"lookout post where Riju is waiting for you.\n"
"\n"
"Riju has told you that a fight with the Divine\n"
"Beast will go much more smoothly for one\n"
"who knows how to sand-seal surf."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_Electric_Relic_Desc"
msgid ""
"The leader of the Gerudo, Lady Riju, asked for\n"
"your help in conquering\n"
"Divine Beast Vah Naboris.\n"
"\n"
"Before you can confront the Divine Beast, the\n"
"Gerudo need help recovering the chief's\n"
"heirloom, which has been stolen. Captain <1.se_co>Teake<2.re_co>\n"
"in the soldiers' barracks has the latest\n"
"information on the thieves."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_Electric_Relic_Finish"
msgid ""
"You've reported to Riju that you've conquered\n"
"Divine Beast Vah Naboris!\n"
"\n"
"You've learned how to use Urbosa's Fury,\n"
"one of the Champions' blessings."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_Electric_Relic_GetBack"
msgid ""
"You retrieved the chief's heirloom from the\n"
"thieves' leader!\n"
"\n"
"It's time to head back to Gerudo Town\n"
"and return the heirloom to Riju!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_Electric_Relic_Invasion"
msgid ""
"You succeeded in taking out all four of the\n"
"Divine Beast Vah Naboris's feet, stopping\n"
"its movement!\n"
"\n"
"Continue your quest by entering Naboris."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_Electric_Relic_Name"
msgid "Divine Beast Vah Naboris"
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_Electric_Relic_Search"
msgid ""
"After speaking with Captain Teake, you learned\n"
"that the thieves are hiding out in <1.se_co>Karusa Valley<2.re_co>,\n"
"but the hideout itself has not been scouted by\n"
"any of the soldiers.\n"
"\n"
"Gather additional information from the soldiers,\n"
"and then head for the thieves' hideout."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_Electric_Relic_Strategy"
msgid ""
"The fight with the Divine Beast Vah Naboris\n"
"has begun. Attack the feet of the Divine Beast\n"
"using bomb arrows to stop its movement.\n"
"\n"
"It seems that staying close to Riju will nullify the\n"
"effects of the Divine Beast's powerful lightning\n"
"attacks."
msgstr ""

